News.Title: Cambridge-PropEquity launch India's first real estate school
News.Summary: University of Cambridge partners with PropEquity to establish India's first dedicated Real Estate School, focusing on AI-driven market analysis and advanced real estate education through specialized programs.

News.Title: Housing sales drop 16% in Q4 across top 9 cities
News.Summary: Housing sales declined to 98,019 units in Oct-Dec period across India's top 9 cities, marking the lowest quarterly sales since July-September 2021, according to PropEquity data.
